---
title: Sweet-Soy Tofu Poke Bowl with Pickled Radish & Sriracha Mayo
description: A tofu poke bowl, we say yes please! A sweet-soy sensation with sesame seeds sprinkled over, this tofu is both tasty and tender. Adding something extra special to this dish is the pickled radish and a generous drizzle of our sriracha and mayo sauce. Dig in!

